# Oracle v2 zipignore — exclude build-time + dev artifacts from upload.
# Runtime-required files (KEEP in zip):
#   - algo_strategy.py, algo.json, run.sh
#   - gamelib/         (engine API)
#   - oracle_core/     (search, enumerator, value, opponent_model, sim_eval, state_adapter)
#   - bundled_sim_rs/  (PyO3 Linux x64 wheel — sim_rs at runtime)
#   - vendored_sim/    (pure-Python sim fallback)
#   - data/opp_model_cache.pkl  (fast opp_model load)
#   - data/citadel_config_snapshot.json  (sim_rs config)
#   - sim_bridge.py    (subprocess fallback; blocked by sandbox but harmless)

# Tests + dev files
*/oracle_core/test_*.py
*/tests/*
*/eval/*

# Docs
*/STATUS.md
*/AUTONOMOUS_LOG.md
*/FINAL_REPORT.md
*/READY_FOR_UPLOAD.md
*/README.md
*/REPORT.md
*/REPORT.txt
*.ps1

# Static binary (sandbox blocks subprocess; useless on live)
*/bin/*

# Output zip itself
*/oracle.zip
*/athena_v3.zip

# Git / OS noise
*/.git/*
*/.DS_Store
*/__pycache__/*
*.pyc
*.pyo
